          <li>Updated the system foundation to a more modern version</li>
          <li>Internal improvements for better stability and performance</li>
          <li>Reorganized windows and overall interface structure</li>
          <li>New visual style and design adjustments</li>
          <li>General fixes and appearance improvements</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
